  "keyFeatures": [
    "Company intelligence on 55M+ startups and private businesses with 250+ data points",
    "People database with 550M+ profiles including founders, operators, and investors",
    "Real-time revenue and profitability signals from news, social, podcasts, and filings",
    "Talent signals tracking new founders, stealth hires, and key job changes",
    "Investor interest signals predicting funding and M&A activity before it's public",
    "Natural language company search across 50M+ entities",
    "CRM integrations with Attio, Affinity, Salesforce, and more",
    "Chrome extension for in-browser company and people insights",
    "REST API for custom enrichment and workflow automation",
    "Specter MCP for AI-native data access in Claude, Cursor, and other agents",
    "Bulk data delivery via AWS S3, Google Cloud, and Snowflake",
    "Revenue and valuation estimates for every company"
  ],
